description: Simulate the invocation of a Method in your RestApi with headers, parameters, and an incoming request body.

parameters.name: restApiId
parameters.description: The string identifier of the associated RestApi.

parameters.name: resourceId
parameters.description: Specifies a test invoke method request's resource ID.

parameters.name: httpMethod
parameters.description: Specifies a test invoke method request's HTTP method.

parameters.name: headers
parameters.description: A key-value map of headers to simulate an incoming invocation request. (string) --- (string) ---

parameters.name: multiValueHeaders
parameters.description: The headers as a map from string to list of values to simulate an incoming invocation request. (string) --- (list) --- (string) ---

parameters.name: stageVariables
parameters.description: A key-value map of stage variables to simulate an invocation on a deployed Stage. (string) --- (string) ---

nested_items.name: body
nested_items.description: The body of the HTTP response.

nested_items.name: multiValueHeaders
nested_items.description: The headers of the HTTP response as a map from string to list of values.

nested_items.name: log
nested_items.description: The API Gateway execution log for the test invoke request.

nested_items.name: latency
nested_items.description: The execution latency, in ms, of the test invoke request.
